item.description:
To create a chronological list of recent edits:<br><pre>&lt;&lt;timeline field maxlength dateformat template:title groupTemplate:title filter:filter&gt;&gt;
</pre>All the parameters are optional:<br><ul><li> <strong>field</strong> determines which field to use as the basis for the list. It is usually <code>modified</code> or <code>created</code></li><li> <strong>maxlength</strong> is an integer that limits the maximum number of tiddlers to include in the list</li><li> <strong>dateformat</strong> is a <a tiddlylink="Date Formats" refresh="link" target="_blank" title="External link to http://tiddlywiki.com/
#Date Formats" href="http://tiddlywiki.com/
#Date Formats" class="externalLink null">date format string</a> that determines the format of the dates</li><li> <strong>template</strong> names the tiddler to use as the template for list entries<ul><li> The default template is <code>&lt;&lt;view title link&gt;&gt;</code> to cause the display of the tiddler title as a link to the tiddler</li></ul></li><li> <strong>groupTemplate</strong> names the tiddler to use as the template for grouping entries in the list<ul><li> The default groupTemplate is <code>&lt;&lt;view %0 date '%1'&gt;&gt;</code>, where <code>%0</code> is the name of the field being displayed and <code>%1</code> is the <strong>dateformat</strong> selected in the third argument</li></ul></li><li> <strong>filter</strong> is a tiddler filter that is used to filter the tiddlers that appear in the list</li></ul><br>For example:<br><pre>&lt;&lt;timeline created 5&gt;&gt;&gt;
</pre>displays as:<br><div refresh="macro" macroname="timeline" params="created 5"><ul class="timeline"><li class="listTitle">15 September 2012</li><li class="listLink"><a tiddlylink="WhatsNew" refresh="link" class="tiddlyLink tiddlyLinkExisting" title="WhatsNew - ericshulman, Monday, December 17, 2012 5:15:00 PM" href="javascript:;">WhatsNew</a></li></ul><ul class="timeline"><li class="listTitle">20 August 2012</li><li class="listLink"><a tiddlylink="MainMenu" refresh="link" class="tiddlyLink tiddlyLinkExisting" title="This shadow tiddler is used as the contents of the main menu in the left-hand column of the screen" href="javascript:;">MainMenu</a></li></ul><ul class="timeline"><li class="listTitle">20 March 2012</li><li class="listLink"><a tiddlylink="TiddlyWiki5" refresh="link" class="tiddlyLink tiddlyLinkExisting" title="TiddlyWiki5 - jermolene, Tuesday, March 20, 2012 3:42:00 AM" href="javascript:;">TiddlyWiki5</a></li></ul><ul class="timeline"><li class="listTitle">7 March 2012</li><li class="listLink"><a tiddlylink="luakit" refresh="link" class="tiddlyLink tiddlyLinkExisting" title="luakit - jermolene, Wednesday, March 07, 2012 8:02:00 AM" href="javascript:;">luakit</a></li></ul><ul class="timeline"><li class="listTitle">14 November 2011</li><li class="listLink"><a tiddlylink="Mathematics" refresh="link" class="tiddlyLink tiddlyLinkExisting" title="Mathematics - jermolene, Monday, November 14, 2011 4:28:00 AM" href="javascript:;">Mathematics</a></li></ul></div><br><pre>&lt;&lt;timeline modified 5&gt;&gt;
</pre>displays as:<br><div refresh="macro" macroname="timeline" params="modified 5"><ul class="timeline"><li class="listTitle">17 December 2012</li><li class="listLink"><a tiddlylink="TiddlyWiki Browser Compatibility" refresh="link" class="tiddlyLink tiddlyLinkExisting" title="TiddlyWiki Browser Compatibility - ericshulman, Monday, December 17, 2012 5:19:00 PM" href="javascript:;">TiddlyWiki Browser Compatibility</a></li><li class="listLink"><a tiddlylink="WhatsNew" refresh="link" class="tiddlyLink tiddlyLinkExisting" title="WhatsNew - ericshulman, Monday, December 17, 2012 5:15:00 PM" href="javascript:;">WhatsNew</a></li><li class="listLink"><a tiddlylink="HelloThere" refresh="link" class="tiddlyLink tiddlyLinkExisting" title="HelloThere - ericshulman, Monday, December 17, 2012 4:08:00 PM" href="javascript:;">HelloThere</a></li></ul><ul class="timeline"><li class="listTitle">28 November 2012</li><li class="listLink"><a tiddlylink="Examples" refresh="link" class="tiddlyLink tiddlyLinkExisting" title="Examples - jermolene, Wednesday, November 28, 2012 1:21:00 AM" href="javascript:;">Examples</a></li></ul><ul class="timeline"><li class="listTitle">25 October 2012</li><li class="listLink"><a tiddlylink="MainMenu" refresh="link" class="tiddlyLink tiddlyLinkExisting" title="This shadow tiddler is used as the contents of the main menu in the left-hand column of the screen" href="javascript:;">MainMenu</a></li></ul></div>

The <code>&lt;&lt;list&gt;&gt;</code> macro creates a list of tiddlers of a given type. It takes the following parameters:<br><br><pre>&lt;&lt;list {type} [template:&lt;templateTiddlerName&gt;] [emptyMessage:"&lt;message for when the list is empty&gt;"]&gt;&gt;
</pre><br>The template tiddlers allows you to customise the text that is displayed about each tiddler. If it is not provided, then the default of "<code>&lt;&lt;view title link&gt;&gt;</code>" is used, which just includes the title of the tiddler as a link. You could add the author to each entry in the list by setting the template to a tiddler with the text "<code>&lt;&lt;view title link&gt;&gt; by &lt;&lt;view modified link&gt;&gt;</code>".<br><br>The empty message parameter allows you to specify text to be displayed if the list of tiddlers is empty.<br><br>The following types are supported:<br><br><h1>all</h1>To list all tiddlers<br><pre>&lt;&lt;list all&gt;&gt;
</pre><h1>filter</h1>List tiddlers that match a certain <a tiddlylink="filters syntax" refresh="link" target="_blank" title="External link to http://tiddlywiki.com/
#filters syntax" href="http://tiddlywiki.com/
#filters syntax" class="externalLink null">filter</a>. The following example lists all plugins.<br><pre>&lt;&lt;list filter [tag[systemConfig]]&gt;&gt;
</pre><h1>Missing</h1>To list tiddlers that have links to them but are not defined:<br><pre>&lt;&lt;list missing&gt;&gt;
</pre><h1>Orphans</h1>To list tiddlers that are not linked to from any other tiddlers:<br><pre>&lt;&lt;list orphans&gt;&gt;
</pre><h1>Shadowed</h1>To list tiddlers shadowed with default contents:<br><pre>&lt;&lt;list shadowed&gt;&gt;
</pre><h1>Touched</h1>Show tiddlers that have been modified locally:<br><pre>&lt;&lt;list touched&gt;&gt;
</pre>
